Package com.github.tadukoo.util.view.form.field

Class BooleanFormField.BooleanFormFieldBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.github.tadukoo.util.view.form.field.FormField.FormFieldBuilder<java.lang.Boolean>
com.github.tadukoo.util.view.form.field.BooleanFormField.BooleanFormFieldBuilder
Enclosing class:
BooleanFormField
public static class BooleanFormField.BooleanFormFieldBuilder
extends FormField.FormFieldBuilder<java.lang.Boolean>
Builder to be used to create a BooleanFormField. It has the following parameters:
BooleanFormField Parameters
Name Description Default Value or Required
key The name of the field (used as a key in Forms) Required
defaultValue The starting value of the field Defaults to null - which converts to false for this field
labelType The LabelType to use for the field Defaults to LabelType.NONE
rowPos The row position of the field Required
colPos The column position of the field Required
rowSpan The row span of the field Defaults to 1
colSpan The column span of the field Defaults to 1
editable Whether the field can be edited or not Defaults to true
Version:
Alpha v.0.2
Author:
Logan Ferree (Tadukoo)
